%%{init: {"theme": "forest"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant S as Serveur
    participant DB as SQLite

    Note over C,DB: Création — POST /api/v1/questions
    C->>S: POST /api/v1/questions<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN<br/>{ type, theme_id, title, choices, correct_answer, level, time_limit, points }
    S->>S: Authentification + Autorisation (admin)
    S->>S: Valider le type (MCQ ou SPEED)
    S->>S: Normaliser et valider le titre (10-250 car.)
    S->>DB: Vérifier l'existence du thème (theme_id)
    alt Thème introuvable
        S-->>C: 400 INVALID_THEME
    else Thème valide
        S->>DB: Vérifier unicité du titre (case-insensitive)
        alt Titre déjà existant
            S-->>C: 409 QUESTION_ALREADY_EXISTS
        else Titre disponible
            alt Type MCQ
                S->>S: Valider choices (4 éléments distincts) + correct_answer ∈ choices
            else Type SPEED
                S->>S: Valider correct_answer (1-40 car.), pas de choices
            end
            S->>S: Valider level (1-5), time_limit (5-60), points (1-50)
            S->>DB: INSERT INTO T_QUESTION_QST
            DB-->>S: OK
            S-->>C: 201 Created { id, type, theme_id, title, ... }
        end
    end

    Note over C,DB: Lecture — GET /api/v1/questions/:id
    C->>S: GET /api/v1/questions/:id<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    S->>S: Authentification + Autorisation (admin)
    S->>DB: SELECT * FROM T_QUESTION_QST WHERE id = ?
    alt Question trouvée
        DB-->>S: Question
        S-->>C: 200 OK (MCQ avec choices / SPEED sans choices)
    else Question introuvable
        S-->>C: 404 NOT_FOUND
    end

    Note over C,DB: Liste paginée — GET /api/v1/questions
    C->>S: GET /api/v1/questions?page=1&limit=20<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    S->>S: Authentification + Autorisation (admin)
    S->>DB: SELECT * ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT ? OFFSET ?
    DB-->>S: Résultats
    S-->>C: 200 OK { data, page, limit, total }

    Note over C,DB: Modification — PUT /api/v1/questions/:id
    C->>S: PUT /api/v1/questions/:id<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN<br/>{ type, theme_id, title, ... }
    S->>S: Authentification + Autorisation (admin)
    S->>DB: SELECT * FROM T_QUESTION_QST WHERE id = ?
    alt Question introuvable
        S-->>C: 404 NOT_FOUND
    else Question trouvée
        S->>S: Vérifier que le type n'a pas changé
        alt Changement de type
            S-->>C: 400 TYPE_CHANGE_NOT_ALLOWED
        else Même type
            S->>S: Mêmes validations que POST
            alt Données identiques
                S-->>C: 200 OK (inchangé, last_updated_at non modifié)
            else Données modifiées
                S->>DB: UPDATE T_QUESTION_QST SET ... last_updated_at = ?
                S-->>C: 200 OK { id, type, theme_id, title, ... }
            end
        end
    end

    Note over C,DB: Suppression — DELETE /api/v1/questions/:id
    C->>S: DELETE /api/v1/questions/:id<br/>Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    S->>S: Authentification + Autorisation (admin)
    S->>DB: SELECT * FROM T_QUESTION_QST WHERE id = ?
    alt Question introuvable
        S-->>C: 404 NOT_FOUND
    else Question trouvée
        S->>DB: Vérifier si la question est dans un quiz
        alt Question liée à un quiz
            S-->>C: 409 QUESTION_IN_QUIZ
        else Aucun quiz lié
            S->>DB: DELETE FROM T_QUESTION_QST WHERE id = ?
            S-->>C: 204 No Content
        end
    end
